<HEADLINE>
GORE CAMPAIGNS FOR VALLONE AND ASSAILS PATAKI 
</HEADLINE>
   (DUPLICATION WARNING: Also filed in category `p')  
 (bl)  
 By RICHARD PEREZ-PENA   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
