but I know that every aisle of Blockbuster has one _ a gritty,
low-budget film about a band of small-time hoods trying to keep it
together, their days dissolving into a mixture of alcohol, drugs,
fights and woman-chasing. Directed by Ted Demme, ``Monument'' at
