<P>
   Here is the CoxNet advance budget for papers of Sunday, Oct. 11.
This budget will be updated every afternoon through the week.
Budget lines include information about what paper originated a
story and whether a story has a related photo, graphic or page
layout. Stories that have photos, graphics or page layouts will be
marked with PHOTO, GRAPHIC or LAYOUT. Those elements will be posted
on the Cox Server in folders matching the category and slug of the
story. All times are Eastern unless otherwise noted.
