   PRIVATE _ A caravan of buses and vans will pull into the back of
James D. Ray State Prison just before dawn Tuesday with the first
50 medium-security Georgia convicts to be locked up by corporate
America. This is the future, for better or worse. (Cook, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
